{"tid":558583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"福岡/北九州 孝子行程求屌","createTime":"2018-02-12T11:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T18:11:47.000Z","uid":79581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d6fc23bff2b4a4a15cbe69e5679ef9ef45c825e7","tid":558583,"uid":79581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:39:48.000Z","msg":"近排轉工撞正UO有平機票買左28/2-7/3 福岡來回機票請埋老母去做做孝子<br />\n諗左成日行程求巴打指點下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n28/2 下午博多落機<br />\n落機 check in&gt;附近鳩行加食晚餐&gt;返民宿<br />\n<br />\n1/3 博多附近行下食下買下野<br />\n<br />\n櫛田神社&gt;天神地下街&gt;運河城&gt;返民宿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2/3 門司港同唐戶市場<br />\n<br />\n8:00 博多JR&gt;小倉&gt; 門司港&gt;搭船去唐戶市場<br />\n14:00 唐戶市場&gt;行返門司港+四圍行&gt;住門司港/小倉<br />\n<br />\n3/3 主要去由布院同住一晚溫泉酒店<br />\n10:30 JR由布院之森&gt;由布院&gt;金鱗湖&gt;入溫泉酒店<br />\n<br />\n4/3 由布院返博多<br />\n<br />\n10:00 由布院JR&gt;博多<br />\n14:00大濠公園&gt;返民宿<br />\n<br />\n5/3 未諗到<br />\n<br />\n6/3 未諗到<br />\n<br />\n7/3 早餐&gt;機場&gt;返香港<br />\n<br />\n依家住要係諗唔到最尾兩日有咩玩 巴打們有冇推介?<br />\n再去 熊本/長崎 會唔會太chur 定係留返係博多附近行<br />\n<br />\n另外所有住宿都未book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人有推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8dd45c197bed3dffb9390a62383a81cc389a32d","tid":558583,"uid":28250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6fc23bff2b4a4a15cbe69e5679ef9ef45c825e7","tid":558583,"uid":79581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:39:48.000Z","msg":"近排轉工撞正UO有平機票買左28/2-7/3 福岡來回機票請埋老母去做做孝子<br />\n諗左成日行程求巴打指點下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n28/2 下午博多落機<br />\n落機 check in&gt;附近鳩行加食晚餐&gt;返民宿<br />\n<br />\n1/3 博多附近行下食下買下野<br />\